 simplicity of\n$\\mathcal{O}[G,P,\\theta]$ if $(G,P,\\theta)$ is commutative and of finite type.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Nov 2013 17:51:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 2 Nov 2014 14:34:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 17 Nov 2014 14:03:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-18"}
