onal methods of studying quantum\nphase transitions, as the promising fidelity approach or the entanglement\napproach, beyond one-dimension and beyond the realm of paradigmatic XY and\nIsing chains in transverse magnetic fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2013 14:53:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Aug 2014 14:27:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 20 Feb 2015 15:37:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-23"}
