 propose a new geometrical model for this region.\nConclusions. The kinematical patterns of the OH+ and CH+ absorption indicate\nthe existence of a layer of mainly atomic gas for which we have derived, for\nthe first time, some physical parameters and its dynamics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Nov 2013 15:56:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
